examples.en: Call me on my cell phone.

examples.ru: Я жду звонка. Мне должны позвонить.

examples.en: They phone each other off and on.
Who was that on the phone?
Have you paid the phone bill?
Is Rachel still on the phone?
The phone bill hasn't come yet.
examples.ru: Счёт за телефон ещё не приходил.

examples.en: Tell me your phone number again.
examples.ru: Повтори-ка мне ещё раз свой номер.
Он резко проснулся от телефонного звонка.

examples.en: Can you get the phone, please?
The phone rang. It was Pam.
The phone box smelt of sick.
You are wanted on the phone.
I had a phone call from John.
He handed the phone over to me.
